    url: "https://arxiv.org/abs/2511.09030"
    abstract: >-
      The foundational paper defining the MAKER algorithm for zero-error
      long-horizon LLM execution via SPRT-based voting, red-flag validation,
      and m=1 microagent decomposition. This implementation is based on the
      algorithms and theoretical framework presented in this paper.
